<body id="page-healthcheck">
    <header_uc:header ID="header1" runat="server" />
    <section class="banner_holder bg" style="background-image: url(/images/home/banner.jpg);">
        <h1>SOLUTIONS FOR TENANTS AND OCCUPIERS </h1>
    </section>
    <section class="pt100">
        <div class="container centeralign">
            <img src="/images/healthcheck/Healthcheck101.png" alt="img" class="second_logo pb50 mlra" />
            <h3 class="pb100 mlra">Just like a visit to your local GP – for your <span class="red">workspace</span></h3>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
			<div class="row clearfix">
            <div class="grid_6">
                <p><img src="/images/healthcheck/Healthcheck101.png" class="p_img" alt="img" /> is a fast and cost-effective solution to get your workforce back
and safely operation as quickly as possible.</p>
                <p>We undertake a study of your premises and provide a suite of solutions that can be
implemented independently or by us on your behalf.</p>
                <p>
                    Subject to current information, <img src="/images/healthcheck/Healthcheck101.png" class="p_img" alt="img" /> can often be undertaken remotely
without physical inspection.
                </p>
                <p>The objective of <img src="/images/healthcheck/Healthcheck101.png" class="p_img" alt="img" /> is to create a set of tools to reopen your office
without having to undertake major physical alterations which can be costly and time
consuming. It enables workforce planning for the short term until more permanent
solutions can be considered.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="grid_6 abs r0 t0 fullheight bg nomargonright  "  >
				<a class="fullwidth abs r0 t0 fullheight bg active_pop_up" data-id="plan_a" style="background-image: url(/images/healthcheck/101_plan_a_thumb.jpg);">			
				</a>
            </div>
            </div>
			<div class="row clearfix">
				<div class="grid_6 abs l0 t0 fullheight bg   "  >
				<a class="fullwidth abs r0 t0 fullheight bg active_pop_up" data-id="plan_b" style="background-image: url(/images/healthcheck/101_plan_b_thumb.png);">			
				</a>
            </div>
			   <div class="grid_6 rightfloat nomarginright">
                <p class="bold fs_medium uppercase pb20"><span class="red">PHASE 1</span> | COVID-19 COMPLIANCE ASSESSMENT</p>
                <p class="bold fs_medium pb20">A 3 Phase program to <span class="red">build confidence </span> and <span class="red">get working.</span></p>
                <p>The assessment phase will involve a compliance review of your current
workplace against government advice and recommendations:</p>
				   
				   <ul class="det">
				   <li>Review of tenancy floor plans to calculate current work zone densities</li>
				   <li>Test compliance with Covid-19 Physical Distancing recommendations</li>
				   <li>Identification of “pinch-points”, shared spaces and congregation zones</li>
				   <li>Review of population circulation and flow</li>
				   <li>Assess business critical functions that require an alternate solution</li>
				   </ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row clearfix">
            <div class="grid_6">
                <p class="bold fs_medium uppercase pb20"><span class="red">PHASE 2</span> | PLANNING FOR CHANGE</p>
                <p class="bold fs_medium pb20">Creating solutions to make workspaces     <span class="red">safe </span> and <span class="red">fun.</span></p>
                <p> Planning work safe changes to allow your workforce to return to the
office in the short term: </p>
				   
				   <ul class="det">
				   <li>Prepare work zone alteration plans to achieve physical distancing and density compliance</li>
				   <li>Identify locations for sanitisation hubs, worksafe signage, maximum population zones, isolation rooms, waiting and separation markers</li>
				   <li>Changes to circulation to minimise close interactions</li>
				   <li>Demarcation zones for congregation points and hot-spots</li>
				   <li>Consider geometry of loose and easily mobile furniture and work settings to improve densities</li>
				   </ul>

            </div>
            <div class="grid_6 abs r0 t0 fullheight bg nomargonright  "  >
				<a class="fullwidth abs r0 t0 fullheight bg active_pop_up" data-id="plan_c" style="background-image: url(/images/healthcheck/101_plan_c_thumb.png);">			
				</a>
            </div>
            </div>
			<div class="row clearfix">
			<p class="bold fs_medium uppercase pb20"><span class="red">PHASE 3</span> | READY-TO-GO TOOLKIT</p>
			<p class="bold fs_medium uppercase pb20"> We do the <span class="red">planning</span> so that your <span class="red">workforce</span> can get moving.</p>
				<p class="pb50">Implementation can be by the client, or we can do this for you and provide a Ready-to-Go Toolkit which can include:</p>
				<div class="grid_4">
				<span class="step one">DEFINE</span>
					<p class="bold pt50">Production of your company branded Ready-to-Go Toolkit for communication with staff to come back to work:
	</p>
					<ul class="det">
					<li>Covid-19 SafeWork Policy</li>
					<li>Planning for Change Employee Guide</li>
					<li>Covid-19 compliant tenancy plans of your workspace</li>
					</ul> 
				</div>
					<div class="grid_4">
				<span class="step two">PREPARE</span>
					<p class="bold pt50">Procurement and installation of any temporary:</p>
					<ul class="det">
					<li>Workzone safety & population signage Sanitisation Hubs</li>
					<li>Physical distancing markers and circulation/ directional markers</li>
					<li>Demarcation of hot-spots and shared zones</li>
					<li>Utilisation marking of furniture and equipment</li>
					<li>Dividing screens and panels</li>
					</ul> 
				</div>
					<div class="grid_4 nomarginright">
				<span class="step three">IMPLEMENT</span>
					<p class="bold pt50">Design and Management of minor fitout modifications:</p>
					<ul class="det">
					<li>Changes to geometry or arrangement of workstations and work settings</li>
					<li>Minor works and modifications to existing fitouts</li>
					<li>Design, coordination and approvals</li>
					<li>Liaison and representation with landlord</li>
					<li>Construction management of any minor on-site physical works that may be required</li>
					</ul> 
				</div>
			</div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class=" pt100 pb100 centeralign">
        <a class="btn mlra">REQUEST A HEALTH<Span class="red">CHECK</Span>101 CONSULTATION</a>
    </section>
